{{Infobox person | name = Katie Stuart | image = | caption = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1985|3|22|mf=y}} | birth_place = [[Vancouver]], [[British Columbia]] }} '''Katherine Anne "Katie" Stuart''' (born March 22, 1985) is a Canadian actress who has appeared in over 15 movies, ranging from the obscure (''[[Atomic Dog (film)|Atomic Dog]]'') to the more well-known (''[[X2 (film)|X2]]''). She has guest-starred on numerous television shows as well as appearing in the television movie ''[[A Wrinkle in Time (film)|A Wrinkle in Time]]''.
Stuart was born in [[Vancouver]], [[British Columbia]] and has a younger brother, Ted. She shares the same name as another former child actress who is best known for her role in the [[independent film]] ''[[Frog and Wombat]]''. Stuart is best friends with the English actor [[Steven Webb]].
